## 3. Readiness Assessment by Domain

For each control domain, assess readiness:

| Domain | Required Evidence | Evidence Status | Gap | Remediation Required | Ready By |
|--------|-----------------|-----------------|-----|---------------------|---------|

Evidence Status: Complete | Partial | Missing | Not Applicable

Domains to cover: Access Control, Data Protection, Incident Management, Vulnerability Management, Change Management, Vendor Risk, Business Continuity, Logging & Monitoring, HR Security, Physical Security.

## 4. Evidence Library Status
